fields.template:
{
  "id": "{{ alertDef.id }}",
  "url": "{{ alert.alertDataUrl | default(value = '') }}",
  "name": {{ alertDef.name | json_encode }},
  "type": "{{ alertDef.type }}",
  "priority": "{{ alertDef.priority }}",
  "status": "{{ alert.status }}",
  "groupByKeys": {{ alertDef.groupByKeys | json_encode }},
  "createdAt": "{{ alertDef.createdTime | epoch_seconds | date(format="%d/%m/%y - %H:%M:%S") }}",
  "updatedAt": "{{ alertDef.updatedTime | epoch_seconds | date(format="%d/%m/%y - %H:%M:%S") }}"
}
